[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿The public transportation in Switzerland is just incredible.",
        "startTime": 5537,
        "endTime": 8245,
        "slowStartTime": 8455,
        "slowEndTime": 12593
    },
    {
        "text": "The ticket system is based on the honor system.",
        "startTime": 8506,
        "endTime": 10741,
        "slowStartTime": 12909,
        "slowEndTime": 16337
    },
    {
        "text": "So after you buy an all-day pass or a one-hour ticket, that's it, you're done.",
        "startTime": 10843,
        "endTime": 15307,
        "slowStartTime": 16415,
        "slowEndTime": 23185
    },
    {
        "text": "No one's standing there to check your ticket at the door.",
        "startTime": 15539,
        "endTime": 18149,
        "slowStartTime": 23459,
        "slowEndTime": 27449
    },
    {
        "text": "Just hop onto the bus or tram and you're good to go.",
        "startTime": 18233,
        "endTime": 20634,
        "slowStartTime": 27499,
        "slowEndTime": 31176
    },
    {
        "text": "I was just baffled by this.",
        "startTime": 20857,
        "endTime": 22850,
        "slowStartTime": 31436,
        "slowEndTime": 34500
    },
    {
        "text": "Obviously, some people take advantage and don't pay for tickets,...",
        "startTime": 22981,
        "endTime": 26021,
        "slowStartTime": 34622,
        "slowEndTime": 39257
    },
    {
        "text": "...but that's why they do occasionally have workers checking for tickets.",
        "startTime": 26142,
        "endTime": 28929,
        "slowStartTime": 39363,
        "slowEndTime": 43619
    },
    {
        "text": "A whole ten days of traveling around and we never got checked once.",
        "startTime": 29125,
        "endTime": 32441,
        "slowStartTime": 43837,
        "slowEndTime": 48887
    },
    {
        "text": "I've heard you can go years without being checked.",
        "startTime": 32564,
        "endTime": 34937,
        "slowStartTime": 48996,
        "slowEndTime": 52631
    },
    {
        "text": "But the one day you figure it's safe to not buy a ticket...",
        "startTime": 35308,
        "endTime": 37995,
        "slowStartTime": 53112,
        "slowEndTime": 57218
    },
    {
        "text": "...because you're only going a short distance...",
        "startTime": 38094,
        "endTime": 39437,
        "slowStartTime": 57291,
        "slowEndTime": 59380
    },
    {
        "text": "...would of course be the day there are two guys on the tram...",
        "startTime": 39573,
        "endTime": 42045,
        "slowStartTime": 59510,
        "slowEndTime": 63293
    },
    {
        "text": "...waiting for you to check your ticket.",
        "startTime": 42292,
        "endTime": 44134,
        "slowStartTime": 63588,
        "slowEndTime": 66426
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's a very serious 100-franc fine if you get caught.",
        "startTime": 44389,
        "endTime": 47691,
        "slowStartTime": 66733,
        "slowEndTime": 71761
    },
    {
        "text": "So, don't get caught.",
        "startTime": 47806,
        "endTime": 50676,
        "slowStartTime": 71859,
        "slowEndTime": 76239
    }
]